name: Magner's Dancing Fingers
description:
The Disco Biscuits played "Pimp Blue Rikki" Live at Fox Theatre in Boulder, CO on 2010-01-31. I shot some fun, shaky video footage, and happened to be right next to Magner on the keyboard during this song.
